@startuml
Example 4 PlantUML:

title Weather Monitoring System State Diagram

[*] --> Registration

state Registration {
    [*] --> SuccessfulRegistration
    state InvalidRegistration
}

state Login {
    [*] --> SuccessfulLogin
    state IncorrectCredentials
}

state LocationInput {
    [*] --> ValidLocation
    state InvalidLocation
}

state WeatherSelection {
    [*] --> Temperature
    state Humidity
    state Rainfall
    state Pressure
    state DewPoint
}

state WeatherDetails {
    [*] --> Alerts
    state WeeklyAnalysis
    state FuturePrediction
    state Graph
}

state Logout

Registration : do / User registration process
InvalidRegistration : do / Registration failed
SuccessfulRegistration : do / Registration successful

Login : do / Login process
IncorrectCredentials : do / Incorrect username or password
SuccessfulLogin : do / Successful login

LocationInput : do / Enter location
InvalidLocation : do / Invalid location entered
ValidLocation : do / Valid location entered

WeatherSelection : do / Choose weather parameter to check
Temperature : do / Check temperature
Humidity : do / Check humidity
Rainfall : do / Check rainfall
Pressure : do / Check pressure
DewPoint : do / Check dew point

WeatherDetails : do / Show additional details
Alerts : do / Show alerts
WeeklyAnalysis : do / Show weekly analysis
FuturePrediction : do / Show future prediction
Graph : do / Show graph

Logout : do / Log out process

Registration --> Login
Login --> LocationInput
LocationInput --> WeatherSelection
WeatherSelection --> WeatherDetails
WeatherDetails --> Logout
InvalidLocation --> LocationInput
IncorrectCredentials --> Login
SuccessfulLogin --> WeatherSelection
@enduml
